:R-HSA-1660517  a           owl:NamedIndividual , obo:GO_0006661 ;
        rdfs:comment        "At the late endosome membrane, the primary event is the dephosphorylation of the phosphoinositide phosphatidylinositol 3,5-bisphosphate (PI(3,5)P2) to phosphatidylinositol 3-phosphate (PI3P) and phosphatidylinositol 5-phosphate (PI5P) (Sbrissa et al. 2007, Sbrissa et al. 2008, Cao et al. 2007, Cao et al. 2008, Arcaro et al. 2000, Kim et al. 2002)." ;
        rdfs:label          "Synthesis of PIPs at the late endosome membrane" ;
        dc:contributor      "Reviewed: Wakelam, Michael, 2012-05-14" , "Authored: Williams, MG, 2011-10-18" , "GOC:reactome_curators" , "Edited: Williams, MG, 2011-08-12" ;
